    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>onion wedges</strong>, the juice of <strong>half<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>your <strong>lemon wedges</strong>, <strong>sliced garlic</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>harissa paste </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Add 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span><strong> </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the dish in the oven for an initial 15 min</p>",
