    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 15 min, drain and add your <strong>king prawns</strong> to the <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, give everything a good mix up and return to the oven for 4-5 min or until the prawns are cooked through – this is your <strong>baked</strong> <strong>harissa gambas pil pil</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
