      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>baked harissa gambas pil pil </strong>with the <strong>roast potatoes </strong>and <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon wedge </strong>and chop your <strong>parsley</strong> roughly over with scissors</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
